Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.40,0:22:23.28,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,300)}chvíľu stáť
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:26.73,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,300)}Dnešnú noc
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.78,0:22:38.46,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,300)}Na chvíľu je to v poriadku,
