Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.98,0:23:17.72,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,300)}Neopúšťaj ma,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.80,0:23:20.63,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,300)}rozplývam sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.11,0:23:24.09,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,300)}Ale deň sa mení na noc
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.11,0:23:27.57,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,300)}Mesačná bohyňa a hviezdny anjeli.
